      "side": 1,
      "message": "This way seems more involved than anticipated. Most of these things should be auto-detected appropriately for the system (target_os, target_cpu), or have no direct bearing on the build’s success (is_debug). It seems like you’re trying to solve a specific problem (obtaining clang) but you’re writing it in the generic development instructions doc as though it’s globally applicable.",
